issues.body:
Annotations like:

```
@JsonTypeInfo(  
    use = JsonTypeInfo.Id.NAME,  
    include = JsonTypeInfo.As.PROPERTY,  
    property = "type")  
@JsonSubTypes({  
    @Type(value = Cat.class, name = "cat"),  
    @Type(value = Dog.class, name = "dog") })  
```

should become swagger subtypes. 
Subtypes should also be added to the model.
